Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:34.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Minami?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:39.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The man who offered to \Nstop the Skrugg's sphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:46.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Dr. Minami is working together \Nwith the NIA to capture the Ghost, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.15,0:01:51.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and he has used that position to \Nseize control of some military units.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:53.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:57.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hughes was the first to notice, and it seems \Nhe is attempting to regain control, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:00.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently Minami has gone completely rogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:04.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:07.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This{\i0} is art in movement!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:10.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,MR-1!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:12.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,MR-1?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:15.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:18.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know your weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:22.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not equipped with \Nany long range weaponry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:27.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I stay outside of your attack \Nrange, there's nothing to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:29.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:38.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:42.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Dr. Minami!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:44.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:46.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This battle ends now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:51.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I get it. Just like you asked...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:54.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll end this battle now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:16.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman has been...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:24.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! I finally did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:29.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is proof that my MR-1 is the \Nmost powerful in the universe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:36.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now there is nothing left that \Ncan stand against my invention!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:56.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman's power comes from electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:04:00.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman was born that night \Nfrom a bolt of lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:04.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And all his techniques so far use electricity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:14.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So no matter how powerful that attack might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:17.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...if it uses the power of electricity...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:20.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's no way that it could defeat Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:25.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:28.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:35.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the perfect distance for Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:37.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:50.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:04:58.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency pullback!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:05.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:11.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnecto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:29.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You annoying little...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:45.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:03.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't keep your distance any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:19.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! I accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:24.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beating you to a pulp at your own \Nspecialty of hand-to-hand fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:29.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,will make the MR-1's victory just that \Nmuch more beautiful and convincing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:38.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on, Ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:46.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Minami, won't you stop already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:49.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cease the fighting at once and surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:50.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:55.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! You are charged with treason!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:57.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What might you be talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:58.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing dumb isn't going to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:00.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better be prepared for the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. I really do apologize then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:10.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...did you seriously expect me \Nto say something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:13.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Minami, you fiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:15.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This conversation ends now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:18.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you people should keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:20.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Secretary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:21.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:27.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Everyone, emergency evasive maneuvers! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:37.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hughes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:40.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Stabilize us already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:44.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! All the electronic \Nequipment is inoperable!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That missile again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:52.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It might not work against the \NGhost, but it sure works on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:57.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, with no more people getting in \Nmy way, I can fight to my heart's content!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:10.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:12.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, it seems they're at it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:15.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, isn't that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:23.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:27.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fling you around and around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:39.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go thinking some chain \Nis going to defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:43.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, can you see what is happening here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:50.20,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,This footage is the scoop of the century, \Nbrought to you exclusively by the All-American Network!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:54.95,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ghost behind the incidents \Nall over the news yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:57.72,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,and a robot created with the intent \Nof getting adopted into the military,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:00.72,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,are engaged in a fierce battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:05.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:09.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! I thought that \Nthere was a press gag order!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:12.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a TV station?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:14.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The press?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:16.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:21.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush you in front of a wide audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:27.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look at the person \Nunderneath the helicopter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:30.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the leading robotics expert, Dr. Minami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:38.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that robot with the giant arms \Nmust be the MR-1, which Dr. Minami created!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:44.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The MR-1 was called in by the military in \Norder to try and stop the Skrugg's sphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:48.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But right before it could be used, \Nthe sphere stopped on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:52.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, it's been involved in \Nthe reconstruction of Center City!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:57.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This robot has been custom reconfigured for battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:59.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and is running wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:04.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand the Ghost has often appeared \Nin Center City helping with the reconstruction,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:07.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and was thought to be an ally of justice \Namong the citizens of the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:12.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to certain "news" reports, \Nuncertainty has grown about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:19.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It was that news about the \Nincident at the reconstruction site!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:28.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Being flung around like this isn't \Ngoing to get Heroman and me anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:11:00.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've come out to a fun place, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:03.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we will decide this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:13.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:17.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At least until you have no where left to stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:19.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:24.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:26.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hughes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.09,0:11:28.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:30.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:35.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I wasn't able to stop Minami myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:40.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. This way the military \Npeople aren't targeting me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:42.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's thanks to you, Mr. Hughes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:51.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Minami can think of nothing else than \Ndefeating Heroman with his own robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:58.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Minami has been plotting all kinds of things to \Nget the MR-1 officially adopted into the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:03.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman defeated the Skrugg before \Nhe was able to face off against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:08.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So he thinks defeating the thing that destroyed \Nthe Skrugg will be the ultimate demonstration.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.59,0:12:12.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he turned Heroman into the bad guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:15.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:20.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He completely loathes Heroman \Nfor taking his spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:22.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.19,0:12:26.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey... I mean, Joseph Carter Jones...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:28.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:32.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an official request from \Nthe NIA, speaking for the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:36.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop Dr. Minami going out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.47,0:12:41.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We want you to destroy the MR-1 \Nbefore there are any more victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:44.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:48.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:51.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:09.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll smash you to bits!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.28,0:13:14.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This time I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:25.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:30.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:35.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:41.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-They fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:44.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:50.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:54.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... His energy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:55.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Joey?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:03.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hughes, I need a favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the Ghost is okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:30.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile the MR-1 is still \Nunderwater, with no sign of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:32.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the battle been decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:36.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Minami has been observing the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:38.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damaged report: check.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:40.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Balancers reconfigured.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:41.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Standby power operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:45.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,MR-1, reactivate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:02.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Commence attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:09.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle has started up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:10.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:11.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:23.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The dam! The dam is being destroyed \Nby the attacks on Heroman from the MR-1!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:25.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good... At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:38.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:46.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:58.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ghost has started using himself \Nto block the MR-1's spears!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:02.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! Even if you protect the damn,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:05.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be trashed to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:11.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:15.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:18.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What could Dr. Minami be thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:20.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dam is destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:23.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it's obvious there will be a large number\Nof casualties from people downstream!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:29.33,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, Dr. Minami continues to attack \Nrelentlessly with the weapon he created
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:32.91,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,while the Ghost, labeled as "evil" by the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:36.35,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,is doing everything it can to protect the dam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:40.32,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a live broadcast that \Nhas not been edited in any way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:44.06,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,What does everyone feel when watching this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:47.06,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only see it one way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:50.82,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,He is not something that threatens humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:55.02,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,He is something that is here \Nprotecting us, being our shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:57.74,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,He, indeed, is our...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:03.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...new hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:09.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn. Out of ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:29.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the final blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:35.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:47.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey... The electricity generator \Nshould be running at full power now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:49.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:52.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, is this really going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:55.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman needs to eat, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:57.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The power plant is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:58.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:00.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:56.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:18:59.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:11.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to blind me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:17.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! Even if I can't see \Nfrom above, the MR-1 can see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:23.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:29.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Minami, above you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:37.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:41.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:29.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it! The Ghost has won!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:40.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heck, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:44.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:48.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:03.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how we stopped being fugitives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:08.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Mr. Hughes all the \Ncharges on us were cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:11.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And thanks to that live broadcast,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:16.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman turned from a bad guy\Ninto an ally of justice overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:18.74,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the connection between \NDr. Minami and the government?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:20.85,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the government really chase down the Ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.53,0:21:21.71,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,No comment! No comment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:26.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the mad scientist Dr. \NMinami and his followers...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:40.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how I returned \Nto my normal, everyday life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:46.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey, could you get me another cup of coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:47.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.44,0:21:51.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:55.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Joey. You look the same as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:21:57.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hughes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:02.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me a coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:08.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.82,0:23:52.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Heroman:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.10,0:23:55.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom is really the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.41,0:23:56.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing better than peace and quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.90,0:23:59.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After the end of their fugitive days,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.20,0:24:02.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey and the others enjoy \Na brief period of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.30,0:24:06.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But in that shadow a new danger lurks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.37,0:24:09.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An unexpected creature appears \Nbefore Joey and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.40,0:24:11.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He gives them a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.30,0:24:15.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Heroman #17: Legacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.95,0:24:18.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman... Attack!
